name: Celebrity Resort
description:
Everyone needs a place to lay their weary head. For travelers visiting Hyderabad, Celebrity Resort is an excellent choice for rest and rejuvenation. Well-known for its proximity to great restaurants, Celebrity Resort makes it easy to enjoy the best of Hyderabad.
Guest rooms offer amenities such as air conditioning, a refrigerator, and a desk, and guests can go online with free wifi offered by the resort.
Celebrity Club Hotel features a 24 hour front desk, room service, and express check-in and check-out, to help make your stay more enjoyable. The property also boasts a pool and an on-site restaurant. If you are driving to Celebrity Club Hotel, free parking is available.
When you're feeling hungry, you can check out Shilpi Family Dhaba (0.9 mi) or Brundavan Family Dhaba (0.9 mi), which are all within walking distance of Celebrity Resort.
Celebrity Resort is sure to make your visit to Hyderabad one worth remembering.
